{"tid":179274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍賣網賣野遇到精神分裂既女人!","createTime":"2017-03-30T06:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T08:22:21.000Z","uid":77228,"like":8,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0f72755ab8bf677c5f6f5faea7d3c022c73a87","tid":179274,"uid":77228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"事情係有條友約我琴日12:45 灣仔地鐵等，我由12:40開始等，但佢手機一直唔通whatsapp又唔覆(只有一個tick)，我等到12:55走左。佢13:00先打比我, 話佢借朋友電話打比我( 電話: 6170 6832)，話佢到了。我話我走左，佢問點唔解等佢，真係好好笑， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢最後話遲d再約。<br />\n<br />\n到13:31 ，佢whatsapp我叫我打比她，我就打，她竟然話她食飯唔聽電話，叫我唔好打比佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明佢叫我打，真係痴線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到今日早上，我收到6170 6832電話，即係佢朋友電話號碼，我起初未睇到，之後睇到就打番去，但又唔通。我就whatsapp佢問佢點樣，佢就開始發脾氣，問我想點，點解我不斷煩佢。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好無奈，明明佢打比我，我只係覆佢一個訊息問佢點樣，何來有煩? 佢今天早上之前從來冇話唔買。我其實一早已經打定輸數怇不會買，根本冇主動再whatsapp 或打比她，佢突然唔買，又發脾氣屈我煩佢..真的不能接受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23u7D79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23u7D79.jpg&h=5f8e5fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rd9S2w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRd9S2w2.jpg&h=0a611489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5Z95RB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5Z95RB.jpg&h=d392fb50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27tSuSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27tSuSz.jpg&h=c533602f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6X7t6Rm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6X7t6Rm.jpg&h=09ce8fd9&s={SIZE}\" /